Separate results on case-by-case basis:
| Case            | Module     | Function          | Duration | Error? |
| --------------- | ---------- | ----------------- | -------- | ------ |
| Normal run      | `etl`      | `load_data`       | 1s       | ‚ùå      |
| Long success    | `modeling` | `train_model`     | 12m 30s  | ‚ùå      |
| KeyError        | `pipeline` | `merge_outputs`   | 5s       | ‚úÖ      |
| NaN ValueError  | `modeling` | `train_model`     | 45s      | ‚úÖ      |
| Micro-task      | `system`   | `health_check`    | 12 ms    | ‚ùå      |
| Monthly retrain | `batch`    | `monthly_retrain` | 12 hrs   | ‚ùå      |


| Feature                     | Description                            |
| --------------------------- | -------------------------------------- |
| `status` column             | Enum flag: `'completed'` or `'failed'` |
| Default                     | `'completed'`                          |
| Auto-set on insert          | Based on whether `error` is NULL       |
| Queries can now filter fast | `WHERE status = 'failed'`              |


