| Use Case                              | Single Table (`profiling_logs`) | Dual Table (`+ profiling_errors`) |
| ------------------------------------- | ------------------------------- | --------------------------------- |
| Real-time alerts on failures          | ‚ö†Ô∏è Costly                       | ‚úÖ Indexed + clean                 |
| Error deduplication & clustering      | ‚ùå Hard to query efficiently     | ‚úÖ Dedicated field structure       |
| OLAP on success/failure distributions | ‚úÖ Easy                          | ‚úÖ Same                            |
| Long retention of errors only         | ‚ùå Impossible                    | ‚úÖ Easy to configure per-table     |
| Joins on traceback content            | ‚ùå Messy                         | ‚úÖ Safe and scoped                 |
